      About this item

      • All-Day Activity Tracking: BIGGERFIVE BRAVE 2 Smart Watch for Kids Teens Automatically counts steps, distance, calories burned, and active minutes. Supports 80 sports modes like walking, running, cycling, swimming(IP68 Waterproof), basketball, and more.
      • Without/With APP: BIGGERFIVE kids fitness tracker watch can be used seperately without APP and phone. But with APP, you could explore more functions. Compatible with Android 6.0+ and iOS 9.0+ smartphones.
      • Comprehensive Health Monitoring: Monitors real-time heart rate and tracks sleep patterns to promote your child's well-being.
      • Customizable Watch Face &1.8" HD Touch ScreenOur kids smartwatch boasts a 1.8" HD touch screen and offers 100+ exquisite cloud dials in APP BIGGERFIVE. Elevate personal style with custom dials using your kids' own photos and ignite their creativity!
      • Puzzle Games under Parents' Control: 5 built-in puzzle games can help train your child's reaction ability and calculation ability. You could restrict your child from playing games at school in the BIGGERFIVE APP (supports also lock game all the time).
      • Encourages Healthy Habits & Perfect Gift Idea: BIGGERFIVE kids smart watch motivates children to develop good exercise habits and stay healthier. Ideal gift for birthdays, Christmas, and other special occasions.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      Amazon Customer
      5 out of 5 stars
      Great first smart watch!
      My 9 year old girls got these watches for Christmas. We all love them! I love that they can use the majority of the features without needing an app. Ive not even downloaded the app yet.They can keep up with their steps and their sleep, and set their own timers for things now. I like that the watch only has five games on it, and I have the ability to control when and how much time they can play those games. So far, the watch does seem to stay charged for around five days at a time. This definitely came in handy when we traveled to not have to keep up with extra chargers. It doesnt come with a screen protector, but I was able to order some generic ones in the correct screen size that are working well. If you want to give your kid a smart watch without all of the extra communication features, I highly recommend this one.

        Reviewed in the United States on February 20, 2025
        Size: Single StrapColor: RainbownylonVerified Purchase
        My 9 year old daughter wanted a smart watch, but isn't quite ready for a real one with calling capabilities. This watch was a great compromise. She was mostly looking for something that would track her steps and this watch seems to be fairly accurate. She's also used the activity tracking features for roller skating and dance to log those workouts, and has worn it to bed to track her sleep habits. I'm not sure how accurate those are specifically because she wears the watch looser than normal, but I love that it seems to motivate her to work on healthy sleep and activity levels. The games are fun for her to play and appropriate for kids. I downloaded the app on my phone so she could choose a wallpaper separate from the handful of pre-downloaded options and the process was simple. We had no issues pairing the watch with my phone and the chosen wallpaper was available immediately after requesting. I like the magnetic charger so there isn't a charging port that can collect dirt and moisture. My only slightly negative thought is that the velcro strap will likely wear out and no longer stick, but it's nice that there are replacement bands available if that happens.
